<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title></title>

    <style>
        h3 { 
            color: #20b075;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .conf{
            height: 50px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .top{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color:#333;
            font-weight: bold;
            height:1000px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .logo{
            text-align: center;

        }
        .bottom{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color:#333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .hr{
            color:black;
            width: 80%;
        }
        .shipping{
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            height: 280px;
            width: 20%;
            margin: auto;
            min-width: 300px;
            max-width: 600px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color:#151515;
        }
        .order{
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: auto;
            height: 200px;
            width: 20%;
            min-width: 300px;
            max-width: 600px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color:#151515;
        }
        .ship1{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: rows;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .bottomText{
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .topText{
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

        <h2>Hi, {{firstname}}</h2>
        <div class="conf"><h3>âœ” Your order {{orderNumber}} is confirmed !</h3></div>
        <p class="topText"> Thanks for ordering with us, we will notify you by email when it will be shipped. 
                You can find below the summary of your order and a receipt in attachments of this email
        </p>
        

        <div class="shipping">
            <div class="ship1">
                <img style="padding: 10px" src="./order.png" width = "28px" height="28px" alt="ship_logo" /> <h4>Shipping information</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="ship2">
                <h5 style="padding-left: 20px">Recipient: {{firstname}} {{lastname}} </h5>
                <h5 style="padding-left: 20px">Street: {{street}} </h5>
                <h5 style="padding-left: 20px">Zip: {{zip}}</h5>
                <h5 style="padding-left: 20px">Country: {{country}}</h5>
            </div>
        </div>

        <br/>

        <div class="order">
            <div class="ship1">
                <img style="padding: 10px" src="./truck.png" width = "28px" height="28px" alt="ship_logo" /> <h4>Order information</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="ship2">
                <h5 style="padding-left: 20px">Model ordered: {{model}}</h5>
                <h5 style="padding-left: 20px">Color: {{model_description}} </h5>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="bottomText"> If you have any questions, please contact our support at team@findmystuff.io </p>
        <hr class="hr"/>
        <p style="text-align:center;"><img class="logo" src="./logo_white.svg" width="250px" alt="logo"/></p>
</body>
</html>